# Loyalty — Internal Endpoints
# UC-023: BFF reads a customer's loyalty balance in a tenant they are not currently
# authenticated against (needed for the switch-tenant tenant list).
#
# Prerequisites:
#   1. pnpm infra:up           (start PostgreSQL + Pub/Sub emulator)
#   2. pnpm --filter @ikaro/backend run migration:run
#   3. pnpm --filter @ikaro/backend run seed
#   4. pnpm --filter @ikaro/backend run dev
#
# REST Client environment: select "local" in VS Code status bar

@baseUrl     = {{backendUrl}}
@internalKey = {{$dotenv INTERNAL_API_KEY}}

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# HAPPY PATH
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Get a customer's loyalty balance in a given tenant
GET {{baseUrl}}/internal/customers/{{customerId}}/loyalty/balance?tenantId={{tenantId}}
X-Internal-Key: {{internalKey}}

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# ERROR CASES
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 401 — Missing X-Internal-Key (global guard)
GET {{baseUrl}}/internal/customers/{{customerId}}/loyalty/balance?tenantId={{tenantId}}

###

### 400 — Missing tenantId query parameter
GET {{baseUrl}}/internal/customers/{{customerId}}/loyalty/balance
X-Internal-Key: {{internalKey}}

###

### Zero balance for a customer with no loyalty data in that tenant (not an error — 200)
GET {{baseUrl}}/internal/customers/{{customerId}}/loyalty/balance?tenantId=00000000-0000-4000-8000-000000009999
X-Internal-Key: {{internalKey}}
